README
===============================================================================

Required modules
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Install npm (node package manager)
https://github.com/isaacs/npm


2. Install the required modules
npm install express
npm install node-config
npm install ejs
npm install socket.io

Example for a npm listing (npm ls)
├── ejs@0.4.3 
├─┬ express@2.4.2 
│ ├── connect@1.6.0 
│ ├── mime@1.2.2 
│ └── qs@0.2.0 
├── node-config@0.0.2 
└─┬ socket.io@0.7.6 
  ├── policyfile@0.0.3 
  ├── redis@0.6.0 
  └── socket.io-client@0.7.3 

If you get the error "Object #<Object> has no method 'bodyParser'" try:
rm -fr ~/.node_libraries/connect
rm -fr ~/.node_libraries/express


3. Clone the repository
git clone git://github.com/eglinetwork/tabletfoosball.git
cd tabletfoosball/
git init
git push origin master


4. Add a configuration file for your development server

How to run
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
node server.js